parameters:
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Kyaiiin! Kyaiiin! Who would have thought there'd be a famous cake shop in such
a remote forest~!
Servant: Right? It's doable, isn't it, Master?

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Kyaaan! I bought so much~n, but I can't eat all of this~n! Because I'll get
fat~n!

Servant: Indeed... we did buy too much. But Master, you're going to eat it all,
aren't you? Despite always saying you'll get fat, you end up eating it all
anyway.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] I will eat it~! Hey, don't you dare take my chocolate parfait~!
Servant: Truly, my Master is such a glutton.
Servant: Ahh, no, it's spilling everywhere.
Servant: It's a bit dirty here, so I'll wipe it off~.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Hey, hey, where are you touching~!
Servant: I'm just wiping off Lady Rade's clothes~. Guhe...
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] You're groping my boobs, aren't you~!
Servant: A little bit is fine, isn't it...
Servant: I'm sorry... Seeing Master made me... aroused...
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] You're committing a crime, you know~.
Servant: Sorry, I don't have a girlfriend, so I just couldn't help it.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Excuse me... who are you people?
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] You're faces I don't recognize. Travelers?
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] I won't say anything~. Servant over there, explain for us~n.

Servant: Are you people from this village? I apologize, we will be leaving
shortly.

Servant: There's a famous cake shop near this forest, and we were just enjoying
some cake here.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Oh, is that so. My apologies.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Let's go home~n, overstaying our welcome is unnecessary~n.

Servant: Villagers, we apologize for any inconvenience. We will clean up the
table before we leave, so please be at ease.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] You, with the pink hair and the prissy way of talking!

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] It's like we don't even exist to you. You seem like you don't want to talk at
all, huh?
Servant: Ah, no, this person is just like that. Please don't mind her.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] It's bothering me~. Why don't you say something?
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Hey, pink hair! What's the idea? Are you planning to ignore us?
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] What do you mean 'ignore~n'? If you say it yourself, it's not ignoring!
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] I'm telling you to wait! Are you making fun of us?!
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Let go. I have no intention of speaking with the likes of you.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] This girl...! (For a moment, my spine froze. This intimidating presence... her
expression and tone completely changed...)

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] !?! (Who is this person? Her expression and tone changed completely in an
instant.)
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] (And this servant seems to be quite skilled too. Just who are these people?)

Servant: So, then everyone, we will take our leave. We apologize for the
disturbance. Please forget about this person.
